{"tid":518251,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"摩連奴：不讓迪布尼上陣是為了他著想","createTime":"2018-01-03T06:31:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-18T19:23:40.000Z","uid":19552,"like":27,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"140c87935a26a3d83844322a5e55a9ba23c4916f","tid":518251,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T06:31:44.000Z","msg":"車路士小將奇雲迪布尼的生活習慣令人擔憂...<br />\n<br />\n車路士領隊摩連奴在對利物浦的記者會上表示，迪布尼不被安排上陣的真正原因是「睡得太少」。<br />\n<br />\n「英超比賽對體能的要求十分巨大。然而，我不希望自己的球員在未得到充分休息時便讓他往場上踢球。」<br />\n<br />\n據說，奇雲迪布尼在每晚都喜歡通宵達旦流連在互聯網上跟網友聊天，當中更不乏英超球員參與，例如隊友艾殊利高爾及曼聯邊後衛畢拿等等。相信他們亦因為相同原因而缺乏上陣機會。<br />\n<br />\n「他每天訓練後總是第一個離開訓練場，並回家睡覺。我不喜歡看見庸懶的球員，更不喜歡體能欠佳的球員。」摩連奴補充說。<br />\n<br />\n奇雲迪布尼於2012年加盟車路士，並於去年被外借至雲達不來梅。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.thedaisycutter.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/233-e1440755920306.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thedaisycutter.co.uk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F08%2F233-e1440755920306.jpg&h=3dd37731&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"49bf59b0dd4248b16c40032aa3d49d7c92ab766b","tid":518251,"uid":143582,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T06:33:46.000Z","msg":"對撚住摩狗俾我都第一個走啦"},{"pid":"d5327e90d9dc21e4ae15b8fb96d38126d5082245","tid":518251,"uid":76403,"like":126,"dislike":0,"score":126,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T06:35:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/03/143548_4103a9daa35b92e885ba99e466aff433.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F03%2F143548_4103a9daa35b92e885ba99e466aff433.PNG&h=70808ac0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d5a3bf88b25475ed34d739f0c985f14fa5e93cb8","tid":518251,"uid":26959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d5327e90d9dc21e4ae15b8fb96d38126d5082245","tid":518251,"uid":76403,"like":126,"dislike":0,"score":126,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T06:35:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/03/143548_410